      "created_at": "2025-03-07T15:30:47.510Z",
      "cooked": "<p>This seems like it would have a high risk of introducing problems.  I think Alex\u2019s idea to keep it simple reduces the risks of issues.</p>\n<p>Use erg to bring HR in range and then hold it.  Use plus minus in the erg section if feeling good or bad that day.</p>\n<p>The biggest issue I have is that I get uncomfortable and need to get off about every 30 or 40 minutes and HR mode doesn\u2019t like that</p>\n<p>Dave</p>",
